name: Situation #4
description:
it was funny and a bit conflicted also feeling silly when you know your parents will pawn the jewels from my grandma even their wedding's ring to get some money for necessary things and pay some bills.
it already happened just like it seems
but why must that thing?

Anyway if it happened to you or no, they just want to maintain the situation of family's finance that i realized after a decade later.
but a couples years ago, i'm glad to have all of them jewels back!
